OL,7,FMore than 20 million people across
OL,8,Fthe UK have faced broadband outages
OL,9,Flasting three hours or more over the
OL,10,Flast year, according to a new report
OL,11,Ffrom Uswitch.
OL,13,FThe comparison site's annual
OL,14,Fbroadband outage study found the top
OL,15,Freason named by internet users for
OL,16,Fthe disruptions they suffered was an
OL,17,Fissue confirmed by their provider,
OL,18,Ffollowed by router problems or
OL,19,Fplanned maintenance in their area.
OL,3,CBroadband outages hit more than 20
OL,4,Cmillion people in the last year,
OL,5,Cstudy finds
